<font color="#FF0000">WE ALL PROTESTED</font><br>
<tt>Tue Dec 24  9:12:39 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
<br>
LEAST WE ALL FORGET, THE PROTESTS IN THIS COUNTRY WERE AGAINST VIETNAM<br>
AND SOME OTHER THINGS AS WELL, BUT ALSO THE<br>
PROTESTS IN THIS COUNTRY WERE BUT A PART OF A<br>
BIGGER WORLD WIDE PROTEST AGAINST ALL DIFFERENT<br>
VARIETIES OF EVENTS, ACTIONS, IDEAS AND PHILOSOPHIES.<br>
THERE WERE RIOTS IN FRANCE, THE CHECHOSLAVAKIAN<br>
UPRISING OF 1968, THE RED GUARDS PROTESTING IN CHINA,<br>
RIOTS IN ENGLAND, AUSTRALIA, CANADA, GERMANY, THE<br>
MIDDLE EAST WAR  OF 1967, TERRORISTS AT THE OLYMPICS, <br>
BLACK POWER, WHITE POWER, BLACK PANTHERS, RED GUARDS,<br>
WEATHERMEN, RED BRIGADES AND WHO KNOWS WHOM ELSE.<br>
THIS PERIOD OF TIME FROM THE EARLY 1960'S TO THE MID 1970'S<br>
WAS WORLD WIDE REVOLUTION AGAINST EVERYTHING THAT<br>
HAD BEEN UP TO THAT TIME.  <br><br>
IN THIS COUNTRY, WE WERE PROTESTING VIETNAM AND THE<br>
PEOPLE WHO FOUGHT THERE, BUT LET US NOT FORGET <br>
THAT THERE WERE AS MANY PROTESTS FROM THE &quot;RIGHT&quot;<br>
AS THERE WAS FROM THE &quot;LEFT&quot;.  THERE WERE A LOT OF<br>
VERY ANGRY AND QUESTIONING INDIVIDUALS DURING THAT TIME.<br>
I WOULD SERIOUSLY DOUBT THAT THERE AS BEEN A PERIOD OF<br>
TIME IN THE WORLD'S HISTORY WHEN THERE WAS REVOULTION<br>
ON SUCH A LARGE SCALE.<br><br>
I WOULD JUST SAY IN THIS TIME OF THE YEAR AND IN THE SEASONS IT BRINGS, <br>
THAT PEACE ON EARTH IS RIGHT AND WHAT WAS IN THE PAST WAS, AND WHAT IS NOW IS.<br>
EVERY PERSON IN THERE OWN MIND WAS RIGHT BACK THEN, BE THEY PROTESTING OR<br>
FIGHTING.  WE JUST HAVE TO ARRIVE AT THE REALIZATION THAT OTHERS HAVE THERE<br>
VIEWS AND LEARN TO ACCEPT THEM.  NOW IS NOW.  WE CANNOT GO BACK AND FIGHT<br>
THE TIMES OF THE 60;S AND 70'S, BUT WE MUST REALIZE THAT WE ALL WERE AFFECTED,<br>
COME TO ACCEPT THAT AND LEARN TO UNDERSTAND THAT OTHERS HAVE BEEN<br>
 AFFECTED AS WELL.<br><br>
HAPPY HOLIDAYS TO EVERYONE WHO WENT, PROTESTED OR DID NOTHING.<br>
W.D.GANZER
<p><code>--   (W.D. GANZER) </code><p>


